; width: 100%;"></div><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetTop Automatic --><div class="KonaBody"><p>WordPress.org now has a <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/top-10">new review system</a> for plugins and themes. While the rating system has always been active, users could never write a review of the plugin. This is especially useful if you&#8217;re planning to give a plugin a low rating.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re using one of my plugins, I request you to head over to the respective plugin review page and write a fair review of the same. If you&#8217;re thinking of anything below a 3, do consider raising your concerns in the respective support forum.</p>\n<p><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/"><img class="size-full wp-image-2032 alignright" title="WordPress" src="http://i2.wp.com/ajaydsouza.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/wordpress-logo-notext-bg.png?resize=111%2C111" alt="WordPress" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></p>\n<p>Below are a set of links of my popular plugins for you to quickly find a link to the review page.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add to All: <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/add-to-all/">Plugin page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/add-to-all">Review page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/add-to-all">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Add to Feed: <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/add-to-feed/">Plugin page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/add-to-feed">Review page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/add-to-feed">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Add to Footer: <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/add-to-footer/">Plugin page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/add-to-footer">Review page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/add-to-footer">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Better Search: <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/better-search/">Plugin page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/better-search">Review page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/better-search">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Contextual Related Posts: <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/contextual-related-posts/">Plugin page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/contextual-related-posts">Review page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contextual-related-posts">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Top 10: <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/top-10/">Plugin page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/top-10">Review page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/top-10">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>TwitterCounter: <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/twittercounter/">Plugin page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/twittercounter">Review page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/twittercounter">Support forum</a></li>\n<li>Where did they go from here?: <a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/wordpress/plugins/where-did-they-go-from-here/">Plugin page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/where-did-they-go-from-here">Review page</a> | <a href="http://wordpress.org/support/plugin/where-did-they-go-from-here">Support forum</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div><div class="shr-publisher-2538"></div><!-- Start Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><!-- End Shareaholic LikeButtonSetBottom Automatic --><hr style="border-top:black solid 1px" /><a href="http://ajaydsouza.com/archives/2012/11/03/review-my-plugins-on-wordpress-org/">Review my plugins on WordPress.org</a> was first posted on November 3, 2012 at 2:44 pm.<br />© 2003-2013 "<a href="http://ajaydsouza.com">Ajay - On the Road called Life</a>". Use of this feed is for personal non-commercial use only. If you are not reading this article in your feed reader, then the site is guilty of copyright infringement. Please 