(1068, 1, '2012-12-30 09:56:22', '2012-12-30 09:56:22', '一、开启\r\n1. 打开wp-config.php文件，在末尾添加：\r\n<pre lang="text" colla="+">\r\ndefine(''WP_ALLOW_MULTISITE'', ''true'');\r\n</pre>\r\n然后上传至服务器，刷新后台界面，你会发现"工具(Tools)"菜单下多了个"配置网络(Networks)"选项。\r\n2. 在进行操作之前，你必须停用所有的插件。\r\n3. 停用以后在点击"配置网络(Networks)"菜单，就出现了如下的安装界面。\r\n4. 简单配置后，然后点击"安装(install)"，进入下一步。\r\n二、配置\r\nStep 1：将 blogs.dir 目录新建于 /data1/www/htdocs/284/qyappsoulsheng/1/wp-content/blogs.dir，通过FTP设置权限777；\r\nStep 2：向您的 wp-config.php 文件（在 /data1/www/htdocs/284/qyappsoulsheng/1/）中添加下列内容:\r\n<pre lang="text" colla="+">\r\ndefine(''MULTISITE'', true);\r\ndefine(''SUBDOMAIN_INSTALL'', false);\r\n$base = ''/'';\r\ndefine(''DOMAIN_CURRENT_SITE'', ''soulsheng.1kapp.com''); //替换成你的域名\r\ndefine(''PATH_CURRENT_SITE'', ''/'');\r\ndefine(''SITE_ID_CURRENT_SITE'', 1);\r\ndefine(''BLOG_ID_CURRENT_SITE'', 1);\r\n</pre>\r\nStep 3：在 /data1/www/htdocs/284/qyappsoulsheng/1/ 中的 .htaccess 添加下列内容，覆盖掉其他 WordPress 规则：\r\n<pre lang="text" colla="+">\r\nRewriteEngine On\r\nRewriteBase /\r\nRewriteRule ^index\\.php$ - [L]\r\n\r\n# uploaded files\r\nRewriteRule ^([_0-9a-zA-Z-]+/)?files/(.+) wp-includes/ms-files.php?file=$2 [L]\r\n\r\n# add a trailing slash to /wp-admin\r\nRewriteRule ^([_0-9a-zA-Z-]+/)?wp-admin$ $1wp-admin/ [R=301,L]\r\n\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -f [OR]\r\nRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -d\r\nRewriteRule ^ - [L]\r\nRewriteRule  ^[_0-9a-zA-Z-]+/(wp-(content|admin|includes).*) $1 [L]\r\nRewriteRule  ^[_0-9a-zA-Z-]+/(.*\\.php)$ $1 [L]\r\nRewriteRule . index.php [L]\r\n</pre>\r\n<a href="http://codex.wordpress.org/WordPress_MU" target="_blank">WordPress_MU官网资料</a>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;', 'WordPress如何开启MU多用户', 'WordPress开启多用户', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e5%bc%80%e5%90%afmu%e5%a4%9a%e7%94%a8%e6%88%b7', '', '', '2013-01-04 07:54:35', '2013-01-04 07:54:35', '', 0, 'http://at.liushousheng.com/?p=1068', 0, 'post', '', 0),
